{
  "stem": "1680.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "So they shot all this 30 people, the kids there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And finally, we arrived in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A Friday night, we arrived in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they took us in in a fancy-- in a fenced place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- and they had a-- a-- a barrack here, which the Judenrat-- you know what the Judenrat was, right?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why don't you tell us about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the-- in-- in-- in Plaszow was a commandant-- a Jewish commandant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had his people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They overlooked, and they walked hand-in-hand with the-- with the-- with [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Goeth. ?] So they were sitting in this room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody has to go by this barrack to go into our own barracks-- has to go there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the meantime, they search what you have.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They searched so that even they opened up the lapels to see if you have something sewed in in the lapels.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they were sitting there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And naturally, they found a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was still around there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And didn't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had money with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had a bundle with dollars and with some jewelry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I know I cannot go through there, because otherwise, they will take it away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Somehow, I managed to overhear-- he was another ordnungsdienst.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He wants that nobody should go to here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But he had an agreement with another ordnungsdienst if he let somebody go through here, he have to pay him off.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So he had a little sign that if you come there, you tell him this and this things, you go through.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I overheard this, so I says to my brother, let's go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I came to this door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I told him this-- this-- this signal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So he says, straight, straight, straight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So we omitted to go there to the search.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
